Q.M., a Minor by his Legal Guardian Lisa Jabbar, Petitioner
v.
GEORGE JUNIOR REPUBLIC IN PENNSYLVANIA CORPORATION, Respondent No. 23 EAL 2018 Supreme Court of Pennsylvania. June 25, 2018

ORDER

PER CURIAM .

AND NOW, this 25th day of June, 2018, the Petition for Allowance of Appeal is DENIED.
